":"ذِى رِيبَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having in it something occasioning suspicion"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]: (Ksh and Bd:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*iY rayobK","text_ar":"ذِى رَيْبٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which means the same: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attended with disquiet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disturbance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"agitation, of mind"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (M, TA:) [see its verb, 4:] it may be from the trans. or from the intrans. verb. (Ksh.)"}],"source_refs":["T","S","A","M","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}